-->
<lb/><p rend="right">19<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> June 
<lb/>1865 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>A telegram just 
<lb/><choice><sic>recieved</sic><corr>received</corr></choice> announces 
<lb/>the death of my 
<lb/>mother so I 
<lb/>start at once 
<lb/>for <placeName>Scotland</placeName> to 
<lb/>help my sisters<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I shall not 
<lb/>remain very 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002341_0002"/><!--pb/@n='80v'-->
<lb/>long but come 
<lb/>back to <placeName>London</placeName>
<lb/>to prepare for 
<lb/>my departure<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Will you kindly 
<lb/>forward any 
<lb/>letters sent to 
<lb/>you to <placeName>Hamilton</placeName><reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">&amp; oblige </p>
<lb/><p rend="center">Yours &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
